staging: unisys: visorbus: Rename #define VMCALL_IO_CONTROLVM_ADDR

Rename #define VMCALL_IO_CONTROLVM_ADDR to VMCALL_CONTROLVM_ADDR, as this
vmcall can be used by any partition, not just the IO partition.

